<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    </head>
    <body>
    	<div style="text-align: center;"><%= image_tag "http://silverandstones.gallery/assets/logo.png", style: "max-width: 450px;" %></div>
        <hr />
        <h1>Hello!</h1>
        <p>Here is your receipt from your order with Silver &amp; Stones Gallery.</p>
        <hr />
        <h4>Order number: <%= @order.id %></h4>
        <h4>Order date: <%= @order.created_at.in_time_zone("Central Time (US & Canada)").to_formatted_s(:long) %></h4>
        <br />
        <h1>Items</h1>
        <table>
            <% @order.order_items.each do | item | %>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= item.item.name %></td>
                    <td><%= item.quantity %></td>
                    <td><%= number_to_currency(item.quantity * item.price_per_unit) %></td>
                </tr>
            <% end %>
        </table>
        
        <p>Please contact us to ensure delivery and payment method.</p>
        <p>You can stop in, or reach us via one of the following methods:</p>
        <p>Phone: (715) 839-8197</p>
        <p>Email: support@silverandstones.gallery</p>
    </body>

</html>
